WEBVTT

01:57.458 --> 02:02.083
Dexter: BLOOD -- SOMETIMES
IT SETS MY TEETH ON EDGE.

02:02.083 --> 02:04.291
OTHER TIMES,
IT HELPS ME CONTROL THE CHAOS.

02:06.875 --> 02:08.625
LAST SEASON ON "DEXTER"...

02:08.625 --> 02:10.250
TONIGHT'S THE NIGHT,

02:10.250 --> 02:12.917
AND IT'S GOING TO HAPPEN AGAIN
AND AGAIN.

02:12.917 --> 02:16.000
OPEN YOUR EYES
AND LOOK AT WHAT YOU DID!

02:16.000 --> 02:17.792
Donovan: PLEASE,
YOU HAVE TO UNDERSTAND.

02:17.792 --> 02:19.959
TRUST ME.
I DEFINITELY UNDERSTAND.

02:19.959 --> 02:22.834
CHILDREN -- I COULD NEVER DO
THAT, NOT LIKE YOU.

02:22.834 --> 02:25.083
WHY?
I HAVE STANDARDS.

02:27.125 --> 02:28.875
YOU'D BETTER BE A COP.

02:28.875 --> 02:30.041
NO. FORENSICS.

02:30.041 --> 02:31.583
THEY FOUND ANOTHER HOOKER.
ANOTHER?

02:31.583 --> 02:33.250
THAT'S THE THIRD ONE
IN FIVE MONTHS.

02:33.250 --> 02:35.125
Masuka: THERE'S NO BLOOD
NEAR THE BODY AT ALL.

02:35.125 --> 02:36.792
IT'S THE WEIRDEST THING
YOU EVER SAW.

02:36.792 --> 02:40.041
I'VE NEVER SEEN SUCH CLEAN,
DRY, NEAT-LOOKING DEAD FLESH.

02:40.041 --> 02:42.750
HOW DOES HE DO IT? HOW DOES
THE KILLER GET RID OF THE BLOOD?

02:42.750 --> 02:44.875
I THINK THIS IS
A FRIENDLY MESSAGE,

02:44.875 --> 02:46.834
KIND OF LIKE,
"HEY, WANT TO PLAY?"

02:46.834 --> 02:49.166
AND, YES, I WANT TO PLAY.
I REALLY, REALLY DO.

02:49.166 --> 02:51.834
Debra: WHAT'S THIS SICK SON
OF A BITCH TRYING TO TELL US?

02:51.834 --> 02:53.667
NOT "US." ME.

02:53.667 --> 02:55.125
INTERESTING HAND JOB.

02:55.125 --> 02:56.834
THINK THIS IS
OUR GUY'S WORK?

02:56.834 --> 02:57.750
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER?

02:57.750 --> 02:59.166
THIS FEELS FAMILIAR.

02:59.166 --> 03:01.333
WHEN HE BROKE
INTO MY APARTMENT,

03:01.333 --> 03:03.709
HE TOOK SOME TIME TO GET TO
KNOW ME, MY LIFE, MY SECRETS.

03:03.709 --> 03:05.417
HE KNOWS.

03:05.417 --> 03:08.250
HE'S NOT CORRUPTING THE HAPPY,
HALLMARK IMAGES OF MY YOUTH.

03:08.250 --> 03:11.208
HE'S REVEALING
THE UGLY TRUTH BEHIND THEM.

03:11.208 --> 03:14.000
SON, THERE ARE PEOPLE OUT THERE
WHO DO REALLY BAD THINGS.

03:14.000 --> 03:15.834
OF COURSE, YOU HAVE TO LEARN
HOW TO SPOT THEM.

03:15.834 --> 03:17.125
BUT I CAN TEACH YOU.

03:17.125 --> 03:20.667
THE CODE OF HARRY,
MY FOSTER FATHER, IS SATISFIED.

03:20.667 --> 03:22.625
HOW THE HELL WAS YOUR DATE
WITH RITA LAST NIGHT?

03:22.625 --> 03:23.792
GREAT.

03:23.792 --> 03:25.583
SHE'S PERFECT
BECAUSE RITA IS,

03:25.583 --> 03:27.834
IN HER OWN WAY,
AS DAMAGED AS ME.

03:27.834 --> 03:29.417
I WANT --

03:29.417 --> 03:30.875
A NORMAL LIFE.

03:30.875 --> 03:32.500
YEAH, A NORMAL LIFE.

03:32.500 --> 03:33.667
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:34.917 --> 03:36.709
THE KILLER IS AN ARTIST.

03:36.709 --> 03:39.041
YOU GIVE ME THE FUCKING CREEPS.
YOU KNOW THAT, DEXTER?

03:39.041 --> 03:40.709
YEAH, I KNOW.
SORRY ABOUT THAT.

03:40.709 --> 03:42.709
WHY,
IN A BUILDING FULL OF COPS,

03:42.709 --> 03:46.458
IS DOAKES THE ONLY ONE
WHO GETS THE CREEPS FROM ME?

03:46.458 --> 03:48.458
I WANT YOU AND RITA
TO MEET MY BOYFRIEND.

03:48.458 --> 03:49.709
DEX, REALLY,
HE'S DIFFERENT.

03:49.709 --> 03:52.458
I FEEL SAFE WITH HIM.
I THINK I'M FALLING FOR HIM.

03:52.458 --> 03:54.333
DEXTER.

03:54.333 --> 03:57.875
I'VE WAITED A LONG TIME
TO MEET YOU.

03:57.875 --> 03:59.709
DAD'S COMING HOME?

03:59.709 --> 04:02.125
IF THEIR DAD SHOWS UP,
WE'LL DEAL WITH IT TOGETHER.

04:02.125 --> 04:04.750
PAUL BENNETT,
FATHER ON PAROLE.

04:04.750 --> 04:06.083
ARE YOU FUCKING MY WIFE?

04:07.083 --> 04:09.250
MY HEART BEATS
FOR THOSE TWO KIDS,

04:09.250 --> 04:12.417
SO IF YOU OR THAT SKINNY BITCH
TRY TO SCREW WITH WHAT'S MINE,

04:12.417 --> 04:14.625
I SWEAR TO GOD,
I DON'T CARE WHO I HAVE TO HURT.

04:14.625 --> 04:15.917
Dexter:
LET'S FACE IT, PAUL.

04:15.917 --> 04:17.417
YOU'VE BEEN A PROBLEM.

04:17.417 --> 04:19.250
IT'S TIME FOR YOU TO GO AWAY.

04:19.250 --> 04:21.291
HE SMACKED ME OVER THE HEAD,
DRAGGED ME OUT OF THE HOUSE,

04:21.291 --> 04:22.875
PROBABLY THROUGH THE BACKYARD.

04:22.875 --> 04:25.667
All I want is for you to look
for a shoe.

04:25.667 --> 04:26.875
It's missing.

04:26.875 --> 04:29.542
I'M TELLING YOU -- DEXTER IS NOT
WHO YOU THINK HE IS.

04:29.542 --> 04:31.709
DO I HAVE THE PLEASURE
OF YOUR COMPANY THIS WEEKEND?

04:31.709 --> 04:34.208
WE'VE HAD A MAJOR BREAK
IN THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER CASE.

04:34.208 --> 04:35.875
DEBRA MORGAN...

04:35.875 --> 04:37.959
WILL YOU MARRY ME?

04:37.959 --> 04:39.250
YES. YES.

04:39.250 --> 04:40.250
WHERE'S MY SISTER?

04:40.250 --> 04:42.625
TOOK HER CODE 12.
LEFT ABOUT AN HOUR AGO.

04:42.625 --> 04:44.625
HOW DID YOU NOT KNOW
WHO I WAS?

04:44.625 --> 04:48.083
I THINK A REAL COP WOULD
AT LEAST HAVE A SENSE

04:48.083 --> 04:52.625
THAT SHE WAS IN THE PRESENCE OF
THE PERSON THAT SHE WAS HUNTING.

04:53.750 --> 04:56.250
WHERE THE FUCK ARE YOU? I'M HERE
AT WORK, AND YOU'RE NOT.

04:56.250 --> 04:59.417
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU. DO NOT
SEE RUDY UNTIL YOU FIND ME.

04:59.417 --> 05:00.792
YOU'RE CONNECTED TO THIS.

05:00.792 --> 05:02.125
I'M GONNA FIND OUT,

05:02.125 --> 05:04.291
AND SOME OF WHAT I FIND'S
GONNA STICK TO YOUR ASS.

05:04.291 --> 05:06.625
I WAS HOPING YOU COULD DIG UP
AN OLD CASE FILE FOR ME.

05:06.625 --> 05:07.875
SURE THING.

05:07.875 --> 05:10.458
IT'S THE CRIME SCENE
WHERE HARRY FOUND ME.

05:10.458 --> 05:13.166
THIS IS WHAT HE WANTED ME
TO FIND ALL ALONG.

05:13.166 --> 05:14.500
HE'S SHOWING ME WHERE TO GO.

05:14.500 --> 05:16.625
LAURA MOSER
AND THREE OTHERS

05:16.625 --> 05:18.625
FOUND CHOPPED UP
WITH A CHAIN SAW.

05:18.625 --> 05:21.166
WHAT IS IN THAT REPORT THAT
HARRY DIDN'T WANT ME TO SEE?

05:21.166 --> 05:23.417
WHAT HE SAW IN THAT
CARGO CONTAINER CHANGED HIM.

05:23.417 --> 05:26.792
YOU WERE LEFT THERE FOR DAYS,
STARVING,

05:26.792 --> 05:28.875
IN BLOOD
2 INCHES THICK.

05:28.875 --> 05:31.208
YOU REMEMBER NOW?

05:31.208 --> 05:33.083
Dexter:
I HAVE A BROTHER.

05:33.083 --> 05:34.166
A REAL BROTHER.

05:34.166 --> 05:36.417
I DIDN'T EVEN KNOW
YOU EXISTED.

05:36.417 --> 05:39.333
IMAGINE HOW I FELT
WHEN I TRACKED YOU DOWN

05:39.333 --> 05:42.291
AND FOUND OUT
YOU WERE EXACTLY LIKE ME.

05:42.291 --> 05:45.166
YOU CAN'T BE A KILLER
AND A HERO.

05:45.166 --> 05:47.291
IT DOESN'T WORK THAT WAY!

05:52.458 --> 05:55.500
WHY ME, DEX?
WHY'D HE CHOOSE ME?

05:55.500 --> 05:57.208
JUST LUCKY, I GUESS.

05:57.208 --> 05:59.625
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]
[ CRIES ]

05:59.625 --> 06:02.583
I WAS SO SCARED.
I WAS SO SCARED.

06:02.583 --> 06:04.834
AM I ONE
OF YOUR VICTIMS NOW?

06:04.834 --> 06:06.125
YOU'RE NOT A TROPHY.

06:07.250 --> 06:09.000
BUT YOU NEED
TO BE PUT DOWN.

06:09.000 --> 06:10.792
[ GAGGING ]

06:10.792 --> 06:11.959
SORRY.

06:11.959 --> 06:14.041
I DROVE AWAY A BROTHER
WHO ACCEPTS ME

06:14.041 --> 06:16.917
FOR A FOSTER FATHER
WHO BETRAYED ME.

06:16.917 --> 06:19.375
I'M NOT ALONE,
AND HARRY KEPT IT FROM ME.

06:19.375 --> 06:21.625
DOAKES ALWAYS SENSED
I WAS HIDING SOMETHING.

06:21.625 --> 06:23.041
NOW HE KNOWS.

06:23.041 --> 06:24.917
MY DEVIL DANCED WITH HIS DEMON,

06:24.917 --> 06:28.041
AND THE FIDDLER'S TUNE
IS FAR FROM OVER.

06:42.250 --> 06:45.333
TONIGHT'S THE NIGHT...

06:51.709 --> 06:56.125
...AND IT'S GOING TO HAPPEN
AGAIN AND AGAIN.

06:56.125 --> 06:58.709
HAS TO HAPPEN.

07:01.750 --> 07:07.458
IT'S NOT WHAT I WANT,
BUT WHAT I WANT DOESN'T MATTER.

07:07.458 --> 07:11.750
THIS IS THE ONLY WAY
I KNOW HOW TO SURVIVE.

07:11.750 --> 07:13.792
[ BRAKES SQUEAL ]

07:16.291 --> 07:19.333
I'M COILED
AND READY TO STRIKE...

07:19.333 --> 07:21.667
[ BOWLING PINS FALLING ]

07:21.667 --> 07:24.041
[ BIG BAND MUSIC PLAYING ]

07:25.750 --> 07:28.208
...ALTHOUGH A SPARE WILL DO.

07:28.208 --> 07:30.542
NICE. NICE.
NICE WARM-UP, BRO.

07:30.542 --> 07:33.333
NOW, YOU CAN GET THAT.
REMEMBER -- LOOSE-ARM SWING.

07:33.333 --> 07:35.291
LOOSE. GOT IT.

07:35.291 --> 07:36.834
YEAH,
AND KEEP YOUR MIND LIMBER.

07:36.834 --> 07:38.583
I'M DOING MENTAL
JUMPING JACKS.

07:38.583 --> 07:39.667
DON'T FORGET.

07:39.667 --> 07:41.250
OKEYDOKEY.

07:41.250 --> 07:43.417
I'M ON EDGE.

07:43.417 --> 07:46.959
38 DAYS, 16 HOURS,
AND 12 MINUTES HAVE PASSED

07:46.959 --> 07:48.959
SINCE I KILLED MY BROTHER.

07:48.959 --> 07:53.250
IN THAT ENTIRE TIME, I HAVEN'T
HAD A SINGLE NIGHT TO MYSELF.

07:53.250 --> 07:55.792
SERGEANT DOAKES
MAKES SURE OF THAT.

07:55.792 --> 07:57.667
HE FOLLOWS ME EVERYWHERE NOW,

07:57.667 --> 08:01.583
A HUMAN BLOODHOUND INCITED
BY THE SCENT OF DARKNESS.

08:01.583 --> 08:03.500
MY BEST HOPE OF LOSING HIM

08:03.500 --> 08:07.166
IS TO ACT
RELENTLESSLY NORMAL, DULL.

08:07.166 --> 08:09.083
SO I BOWL.

08:13.041 --> 08:14.458
[ CHEERING ]

08:14.458 --> 08:16.959
WHAT'S REALLY DISTURBING IS
THAT I'M GOOD AT IT.

08:16.959 --> 08:19.333
BALLS, DEX.

08:19.333 --> 08:20.667
PICTURED IT,
DIDN'T YOU?

08:25.333 --> 08:28.083
HEY, STRIKER, WE NEED YOU
TO LOCK DOWN TONIGHT, HUH?

08:28.083 --> 08:30.041
WE'RE PLAYING
THE ALLEY CATS.

08:30.041 --> 08:31.333
[ SIGHS ]

08:31.333 --> 08:34.500
I'M A LITTLE TENSE,
ANGEL.

08:34.500 --> 08:37.583
BUT I'LL TRY MY BEST
NOT TO LET THE TEAM DOWN.

08:37.583 --> 08:40.417
TRY, DEXTER? TRY?

08:40.417 --> 08:41.709
YOU GOT TO THINK POSITIVE,
BRO,

08:41.709 --> 08:44.458
'CAUSE WHAT WE THINK CREATES
THE WORLD AROUND US.

08:44.458 --> 08:46.834
IT'S ALL ABOUT ENERGY
AND INTERCONNECTEDNESS.

08:46.834 --> 08:48.917
I MEAN,
WE GOT TO THINK POSITIVE...

08:48.917 --> 08:51.709
ANGEL LOST SOMEONE, TOO,
WHEN HIS WIFE LEFT HIM.

08:51.709 --> 08:53.291
NOW HE'S GOING
TOWARD THE LIGHT,

08:53.291 --> 08:55.083
SEARCHING FOR ANSWERS.

08:55.083 --> 08:57.709
HE FOUND ONE
ON AN "OPRAH" RERUN.

08:57.709 --> 08:59.834
I WISH IT WERE
THAT EASY FOR ME.

08:59.834 --> 09:03.083
AND WE JUST GOT TO DIRECT IT
TO MANIFEST WHAT WE WANT.

09:03.083 --> 09:04.709
OKAY?

09:04.709 --> 09:06.208
ALL RIGHT.

09:11.291 --> 09:14.208
[ LATIN MUSIC PLAYING ]

09:18.375 --> 09:21.041
[ CHEERING ]

09:21.041 --> 09:22.709
DUDE,
DUDE, JUST BOWL A STRIKE

09:22.709 --> 09:25.375
SO WE CAN GO HAVE SOME FUN
AT THE STRIP CLUBS.

09:25.375 --> 09:27.291
I WANT TO SEE
A REAL 7-10 SPLIT.

09:27.291 --> 09:28.792
I WISH I COULD HAVE FUN.

09:28.792 --> 09:30.208
WITH DOAKES TAILING ME,

09:30.208 --> 09:32.542
MY LIFE'S BEEN ALL JEKYLL
AND NO HYDE --

09:32.542 --> 09:34.000
NO MOONLIT PLAYDATES,

09:34.000 --> 09:37.125
NO LATE-NIGHT SOCIAL CALLS,
NOT ONE.

09:37.125 --> 09:39.625
MY BROTHER WOULD BE
SO DISAPPOINTED.

09:39.625 --> 09:42.959
DON'T FORGET --
TELL THE UNIVERSE WHAT YOU NEED.

09:42.959 --> 09:46.250
I REALLY NEED
TO KILL SOMEBODY.

09:50.625 --> 09:53.250
[ CHEERING ]
[ GROANING ]

09:58.417 --> 10:01.500
DID YOU EVEN
TAKE MY ADVICE, JOSE?

10:01.500 --> 10:04.750
I'M TELLING YOU -- THE UNIVERSE
CAN BE VERY GENEROUS.

10:16.166 --> 10:19.875
IT CERTAINLY CAN.

10:22.125 --> 10:26.667
FOR WEEKS I'VE KNOWN WHO WAS
NEXT, WHO BELONGED TO ME.

10:26.667 --> 10:30.166
I JUST NEEDED DOAKES
TO TAKE A NIGHT OFF.

10:30.166 --> 10:32.667
[ CLUCKING ]

10:36.291 --> 10:39.083
[ CHIMES RINGING ]

10:41.542 --> 10:43.417
WHAT DO YOU NEED?

10:45.166 --> 10:48.583
I NEED TO, UH,
CURSE SOMEONE.

10:48.583 --> 10:50.917
[ LAUGHS ]
WHAT KIND OF CURSE?

10:53.250 --> 10:54.792
[ LOCK CLICKS ]

10:54.792 --> 10:55.917
DEATH CURSE.

10:59.000 --> 11:02.083
WE DON'T DO THAT KIND
OF THING HERE.

11:02.083 --> 11:03.834
YOU CAN GO DOWN
TO LITTLE HAITI,

11:03.834 --> 11:06.625
FIND ALL THE HOODOO VOODOO
YOU NEED THERE.

11:08.000 --> 11:12.166
YOU ARE JIMMY SENSIO,
HIGH PRIEST, RIGHT?

11:15.792 --> 11:19.500
THE MAN WITH GOD
IN HIS MOUTH?

11:19.500 --> 11:23.083
I'M NOT A TOURIST.

11:23.083 --> 11:26.458
I NEED A PETRO CURSE,
AND I HEARD YOU WERE THE BEST.

11:27.917 --> 11:31.041
THANK YOU
FOR YOUR OFFERING.

11:31.041 --> 11:31.959
COME.

11:46.500 --> 11:47.792
[ GROANS ]

11:51.709 --> 11:54.417
A BLIND MAN --
NOT VERY SPORTING, I KNOW,

11:54.417 --> 11:57.291
BUT I'M NOT ONE TO DISCRIMINATE
BASED ON RACE,

11:57.291 --> 11:59.709
GENDER, OR DISABILITY.

12:01.625 --> 12:04.208
[ GASPS ]

12:04.208 --> 12:08.875
WHAT...IS...HAPPENING?

12:08.875 --> 12:12.709
THE ONLY PERTINENT QUESTION IS
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOUR VICTIMS?

12:12.709 --> 12:14.375
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

12:14.375 --> 12:15.750
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

12:15.750 --> 12:17.959
I CAN SEE HOW THIS MIGHT
BE CONFUSING FOR YOU, JIMMY,

12:17.959 --> 12:19.959
BUT MY FAVORITE PART'S
KIND OF RUINED HERE.

12:19.959 --> 12:21.750
SEE, THIS IS WHERE
I NORMALLY SHOW YOU

12:21.750 --> 12:23.959
THE INNOCENT PEOPLE
YOU'VE KILLED.

12:23.959 --> 12:27.000
I BROUGHT THEM ALONG ANYWAY,
AS PART OF MY DEATH RITUAL.

12:27.000 --> 12:29.875
SINCE YOU'RE BLIND,
I'LL JUST REMIND YOU.

12:29.875 --> 12:32.875
EMMANUEL ALZUA,

12:32.875 --> 12:34.625
JEAN PHILIPPE PEGUERO,

12:34.625 --> 12:36.709
NONO BAPTISTE.

12:36.709 --> 12:39.000
I DIDN'T KILL THEM.
I CURSED THEM.

12:39.000 --> 12:41.291
AND IN A REMARKABLE
COINCIDENCE,

12:41.291 --> 12:43.667
THEY EACH DIED
OF RESPIRATORY FAILURE

12:43.667 --> 12:45.125
WITH FLUID
IN THEIR LUNGS.

12:45.125 --> 12:48.417
I GUESS MURDER IS ONE WAY
TO MAKE YOUR CURSES COME TRUE.

12:48.417 --> 12:49.583
IT'S GOOD FOR BUSINESS.

12:49.583 --> 12:51.959
[ GROANING ]

12:51.959 --> 12:53.667
WHAT? WHAT WAS THAT?

12:53.667 --> 12:55.959
JUST THE NEXT PART
OF THE RITUAL.

12:57.125 --> 13:00.250
HOW DID YOU ADMINISTER THE RICIN
POISON TO YOUR VICTIMS?

13:00.250 --> 13:03.917
[ GROANING ]

13:03.917 --> 13:06.083
[ GAGGING ]

13:06.083 --> 13:10.208
[ Hoarsely ] I AM THE ONE
WITH THE POWER IN HIS HANDS.

13:11.583 --> 13:13.750
THAT'S NOT ENTIRELY
ACCURATE.

13:13.750 --> 13:15.959
THOSE WHO BELIEVE IN ME
SHALL BE FREE.

13:15.959 --> 13:18.333
ALABANZA, ALABAN--

13:18.333 --> 13:19.333
KNOCK IT OFF.

13:19.333 --> 13:20.834
HOW'D YOU POISON THEM?

13:20.834 --> 13:22.625
[ PANTING ]

13:22.625 --> 13:24.750
[ Normal voice ] NOT ME.

13:24.750 --> 13:29.417
MADOLI, MY PETRO SPIRIT,
TOLD ME PUT THE POWDER

13:29.417 --> 13:33.875
IN THE AGUARDIENTE BOTTLES
THAT THEY BUY FROM ME.

13:33.875 --> 13:36.458
AND I DID IT.

13:36.458 --> 13:38.083
THANK YOU, JIMMY.

13:38.083 --> 13:40.709
MY RITUAL'S ALMOST
COMPLETE.

13:40.709 --> 13:43.000
[ Hoarsely ]
MADOLI CURSES YOU! YOU --

13:43.000 --> 13:47.083
I'M AFRAID MADOLI'S A LITTLE
LATE TO THE PARTY ON THAT ONE.

13:49.500 --> 13:51.375
[ WHIMPERING ]

13:51.375 --> 13:54.250
I APPRECIATE YOU HELPING ME OUT
TONIGHT, JIMMY.

13:54.250 --> 13:57.166
I'VE BEEN WAITING A LONG TIME
FOR THIS.

13:57.166 --> 13:58.500
[ SOBS ]

13:58.500 --> 14:00.625
I REALLY NEEDED IT.

14:03.250 --> 14:05.208
[ CHICKENS CLUCKING ]

14:11.500 --> 14:13.125
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

14:14.500 --> 14:15.625
[ CHICKENS SQUAWK ]

14:18.542 --> 14:21.625
[ Sighing ]
WHAT THE FUCK?

14:39.667 --> 14:41.709
LET THAT BE A LESSON TO YOU.

14:41.709 --> 14:44.166
I'VE ALWAYS ENJOYED MY WORK.

14:44.166 --> 14:48.208
IT BRINGS ORDER TO THE CHAOS,
FILLS ME WITH CIVIC PRIDE.

14:48.208 --> 14:50.417
BUT WHAT WAS THAT BACK THERE?

14:50.417 --> 14:51.709
NOT VOODOO.

14:51.709 --> 14:53.041
WHEN I PICKED UP THE KNIFE,

14:53.041 --> 14:55.625
IT'S LIKE I DIDN'T KNOW
WHO I WAS.

14:55.625 --> 14:57.667
I COME HERE TO DUMP BODIES,
NOT BEER BOTTLES.

14:57.667 --> 14:59.875
NOW I'M JUST A LITTERBUG.

15:20.959 --> 15:22.750
DEB!

15:28.291 --> 15:30.333
JESUS!

15:30.333 --> 15:32.792
WHAT ARE YOU DOING WORKING OUT
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT?

15:32.792 --> 15:34.291
I COULDN'T SLEEP.

15:34.291 --> 15:36.750
TOMORROW'S YOUR BIG DAY.

15:38.625 --> 15:41.583
WHERE THE FUCK WERE YOU?
I WAS WORRIED ABOUT YOU.

15:41.583 --> 15:42.583
BOWLING.

15:42.583 --> 15:44.667
KIND OF LATE FOR BOWLING.

15:44.667 --> 15:46.959
KIND OF NOT LOOKING
FOR YOUR OPINION.

15:46.959 --> 15:49.250
YOU SAID YOU CLEANED
THE PLACE TODAY?

15:49.250 --> 15:51.166
I DID.
IT GOT MESSED UP AGAIN.

15:51.166 --> 15:54.208
I DON'T SUPPOSE YOU WERE LOOKING
AT APARTMENT-RENTAL ADS

15:54.208 --> 15:56.125
WHILE YOU WERE
ON THE TREADMILL?

15:56.125 --> 15:58.625
LOOK, IF YOU WANT ME
OUT OF HERE, JUST --

15:58.625 --> 16:00.291
I DON'T.
I JUST HAD A BAD...

16:00.291 --> 16:03.250
[ SIGHS ]
...BOWLING NIGHT.

16:03.250 --> 16:06.000
WHAT I MEANT WAS, WHENEVER
YOU'RE READY TO BE ON YOUR OWN,

16:06.000 --> 16:08.333
I'LL HELP YOU
WITH THE TRANSITION, THAT'S ALL.

16:08.333 --> 16:11.125
THANKS, DEX.

16:11.125 --> 16:14.250
THANKS FOR PUTTING UP
WITH ME.

16:14.250 --> 16:16.917
YOU'RE ALL I GOT.

16:16.917 --> 16:21.291
THAT'S NOT SUCH A GREAT BARGAIN
FOR YOU, HUH?

16:21.291 --> 16:24.417
I'M NOT COMPLAINING.

16:25.792 --> 16:27.500
NIGHT.

16:27.500 --> 16:28.834
IT'S YOUR TURN ON THE COUCH.

16:28.834 --> 16:30.834
COULD YOU AT LEAST
PICK UP YOUR --

16:30.834 --> 16:33.083
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

16:33.083 --> 16:36.041
DEBRA CAN'T SLEEP
IN AN EMPTY HOUSE ANYMORE.

16:36.041 --> 16:37.792
IN FACT, SHE CAN'T SLEEP
MUCH AT ALL.

16:37.792 --> 16:39.208
I GUESS THAT'S WHAT HAPPENS

16:39.208 --> 16:41.333
WHEN YOUR FIANCé
TRIES TO SLICE YOU UP

16:41.333 --> 16:44.166
INTO SMALL, BLOODLESS PIECES.

16:47.000 --> 16:48.041
PATHETIC.

16:55.041 --> 16:57.000
[ GUNSHOT ]

16:57.000 --> 16:58.417
[ CHUCKLES ]

16:58.417 --> 16:59.792
DID YOU SEE THAT?

16:59.792 --> 17:01.542
THAT'S NICE SHOOTING, DEX.
WE NEED TO TALK.

17:01.542 --> 17:04.166
THOSE BOARS DON'T STAND
A CHANCE. HOPE ONE CHARGES ME.

17:04.166 --> 17:05.417
NO, YOU DON'T, DEX.
LISTEN --

17:05.417 --> 17:07.000
THIS THING'S GOT MASSIVE
STOPPING POWER.

17:07.000 --> 17:09.000
DEXTER, SLOW DOWN.
I GOT BAD NEWS.

17:09.000 --> 17:11.166
THEY NEED ME TO TAKE A SHIFT
AT WORK.

17:11.166 --> 17:14.041
RIGHT NOW? BUT WHAT ABOUT
THE BOAR HUNT?

17:14.041 --> 17:15.834
WE'LL PLAN ANOTHER TRIP.

17:15.834 --> 17:17.166
I WAITED TWO WEEKS
FOR THIS TRIP.

17:17.166 --> 17:18.959
YOU CAN WAIT ANOTHER ONE.
NO, I CAN'T.

17:18.959 --> 17:21.709
IF YOU READ THE BOOKS, YOU'D
KNOW THAT PSYCHOPATHS LIKE ME

17:21.709 --> 17:23.792
HAVE A LOW TOLERANCE
FOR FRUSTRATION.

17:23.792 --> 17:25.542
DEXTER, ENOUGH WITH
THE PSYCHOPATH BULLSHIT.

17:25.542 --> 17:27.875
YOU'RE IN CONTROL OF YOUR URGES,
NOT THE OTHER WAY AROUND.

17:27.875 --> 17:30.917
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND, DAD.
I NEED THIS.

17:30.917 --> 17:32.875
IT'S NOT JUST
A SPORT TO ME.

17:32.875 --> 17:35.709
I'M SORRY, SON.
I HAVE RESPONSIBILITIES AT WORK.

17:35.709 --> 17:37.166
NOW, COME ON.

17:37.166 --> 17:39.417
I'LL DROP YOU OFF AT HOME.
GIVE ME THE GUN.

17:39.417 --> 17:40.542
NO!

17:40.542 --> 17:42.041
[ GUNSHOT ]

17:53.083 --> 17:55.875
THERE'S CHEESE
IN THAT DOUGHNUT.

17:55.875 --> 17:57.834
OH, THAT'S A DANISH.

17:57.834 --> 18:01.333
LOOK, THEY FORGOT THE FROSTING
ON THIS ONE.

18:01.333 --> 18:05.208
WELL, SOME PEOPLE LIKE DOUGHNUTS
PLAIN, NO FROSTING.

18:07.291 --> 18:09.542
I CAN'T EVEN GET DOUGHNUTS
RIGHT. WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

18:11.417 --> 18:14.208
SORRY, GUYS, I WAS IN A HURRY.
I JUST ORDERED A DOZEN.

18:14.208 --> 18:16.625
PASTRY BUFFS LIKE YOU TWO
DESERVE BETTER THAN THIS.

18:16.625 --> 18:19.000
THANKS, DEXTER.

18:19.000 --> 18:22.041
WE'RE GONNA GO VISIT MY DAD
IN JAIL TODAY.

18:22.041 --> 18:23.291
YOU WANT TO COME?

18:23.291 --> 18:26.041
AFRAID I GOT TO WORK,
BUDDY.

18:26.041 --> 18:28.667
OKAY.

18:28.667 --> 18:30.583
THANKS FOR GETTING HERE
SO FAST.

18:30.583 --> 18:31.750
WHAT'S THE EMERGENCY?

18:31.750 --> 18:33.542
"HIP HOP HARRY" IS ON.

18:33.542 --> 18:35.333
♪ HIP HOP  ♪
♪ HARRY  ♪

18:35.333 --> 18:37.667
♪ WHEN I SAY, "HIP HOP,"
YOU SAY, "HARRY"  ♪

18:37.667 --> 18:38.792
♪ HIP HOP  ♪
♪ HARRY  ♪

18:38.792 --> 18:40.917
♪ HIP HOP, IT'S ON!  ♪

18:45.917 --> 18:48.333
WE'RE GOOD
FOR 15 MINUTES.

18:50.583 --> 18:52.750
[ SIGHS ]

18:52.750 --> 18:55.041
I KNOW WE'RE SUPPOSED TO HAVE
DINNER TONIGHT,

18:55.041 --> 18:57.250
BUT I JUST HAD THIS URGE.

18:59.750 --> 19:02.083
I'M ALL FOR
SATISFYING URGES.

19:02.083 --> 19:03.291
I JUST WISH I KNEW

19:03.291 --> 19:06.458
WHY I COULDN'T SATISFY MINE
LAST NIGHT.

19:06.458 --> 19:08.667
[ MOANING ]

19:22.709 --> 19:23.917
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

19:23.917 --> 19:25.542
YEAH, IT WILL BE.
JUST KEEP GOING.

19:25.542 --> 19:27.166
OKAY.

19:28.667 --> 19:31.458
ANY MINUTE NOW.

19:40.583 --> 19:42.625
[ SIGHS ]

19:42.625 --> 19:44.125
SORRY.

19:44.125 --> 19:46.208
NO. NO, IT'S MY FAULT.

19:46.208 --> 19:49.583
I SHOULDN'T BE SPRINGING THIS
ON YOU.

19:49.583 --> 19:51.333
NO, IT'S NOT THAT.

19:51.333 --> 19:55.333
I'M JUST FEELING
A LITTLE PRESSURE AT WORK.

19:55.333 --> 19:58.125
[ SIGHS ]

20:01.667 --> 20:03.000
I'LL BE OKAY.

20:03.000 --> 20:06.500
I FOLLOWED THE CODE.
THE STALK WAS GOOD.

20:06.500 --> 20:10.291
I'M JUST A LITTLE RUSTY
SINCE KILLING MY BROTHER.

20:10.291 --> 20:14.208
OR MAYBE I TOOK PITY
ON MY VICTIM.

20:14.208 --> 20:16.083
I MEAN, SURE,
HE'S A HEINOUS KILLER,

20:16.083 --> 20:18.250
BUT HE ALSO BUMPS INTO WALLS.

20:23.417 --> 20:25.166
HEY, SERGEANT.

20:25.166 --> 20:28.083
THANKS FOR SUPPORTING
THE BOWLING TEAM.

20:28.083 --> 20:29.417
FUCK YOU.

20:29.417 --> 20:31.250
WHERE'S MY BLOOD REPORT
ON THE MAYNARD VICTIM?

20:34.625 --> 20:37.375
SO, WHAT'S THAT,
A TITTY SITE?

20:38.834 --> 20:40.542
OOPS, CAUGHT ME.

20:40.542 --> 20:43.834
BULLSHIT. WHAT THE HELL
WERE YOU REALLY DOING IN HERE?

20:43.834 --> 20:45.709
THE TITS ARE RIGHT THERE.

20:45.709 --> 20:47.166
YEAH, BUT IN 10 YEARS,

20:47.166 --> 20:49.750
YOU'VE NEVER RENTED
A SINGLE PORN TITLE.

20:52.709 --> 20:55.417
HUH.
HOW WOULD YOU KNOW?

20:57.250 --> 20:58.583
CALL ME AN OFFICE CRAZY,

20:58.583 --> 21:01.417
BUT YOUR HUMBLING INTEREST
IN MY PERSONAL LIFE

21:01.417 --> 21:04.500
COULD BE MISINTERPRETED
AS HARASSMENT IN SOME CIRCLES.

21:04.500 --> 21:07.166
SO REPORT ME.

21:07.166 --> 21:09.542
I COULD THINK
OF EASIER SOLUTIONS.

21:11.250 --> 21:13.542
NICE TITS.

21:20.291 --> 21:22.458
JAMES, YOU GOT
ANY MISDEMEANOR "A" FORMS?

21:22.458 --> 21:24.250
TRY THE FILING CABINET.

21:26.417 --> 21:28.458
CAN ANYBODY TELL ME

21:28.458 --> 21:31.625
WHERE THE GODDAMN
MISDEMEANOR "A" FORMS ARE KEPT?

21:31.625 --> 21:34.250
I'VE GOT SOME RIGHT HERE,
LIEUTENANT.

21:34.250 --> 21:35.375
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

21:35.375 --> 21:37.083
OKAY, ALL RIGHT,
MOVE ALONG.

21:37.083 --> 21:40.417
NOTHING TO SEE HERE, JUST
ANOTHER FUCKING DAY AT WORK.

21:46.458 --> 21:48.625
WELCOME BACK, MORGAN.

21:48.625 --> 21:50.667
THANKS.

21:53.458 --> 21:54.583
MARIA.

22:02.834 --> 22:06.000
A TOUR-BOAT GUIDE CALLED IN
A BODY DOWN AT THE BREAKWATER.

22:06.000 --> 22:08.458
I WANT YOU TO TAKE DOAKES
AND A SUPPORT TEAM

22:08.458 --> 22:10.000
AND TAKE MORGAN.

22:10.000 --> 22:13.000
I WANT TO GET HER BACK OUT
IN THE FIELD TODAY.

22:13.000 --> 22:14.125
HMM. SHE'S NOT READY.

22:14.125 --> 22:16.166
SHE SHOULDN'T EVEN BE HERE.

22:16.166 --> 22:17.792
WHAT'S IT BEEN --
FIVE WEEKS, SIX?

22:17.792 --> 22:19.041
I APPRECIATE YOUR CONCERN,

22:19.041 --> 22:20.959
BUT ACCORDING
TO HER PSYCH EVALUATION,

22:20.959 --> 22:23.000
SHE'S READY TO GET BACK OUT
INTO THE FIELD.

22:23.000 --> 22:25.583
YOU JUST GOT TO LOOK HER
IN THE EYES

22:25.583 --> 22:27.333
TO KNOW SHE'S NOT RIGHT.

22:27.333 --> 22:30.792
YOU PUT HER OUT IN THE FIELD,
SHE COULD MELT DOWN, FREAK OUT.

22:32.208 --> 22:33.500
SHE HUGGED ME.

22:33.500 --> 22:36.583
ALL RIGHT, WELL,
YOU PARTNER WITH HER TODAY

22:36.583 --> 22:38.333
SO YOU CAN KEEP
AN EYE ON HER.

22:38.333 --> 22:39.583
THAT'S --
NOT A REQUEST.

22:39.583 --> 22:41.458
PUT DOAKES WITH BATISTA.

22:44.667 --> 22:48.125
FINE.

22:48.125 --> 22:50.625
MARIA...

22:50.625 --> 22:53.125
I KNOW THAT IT'S DIFFICULT
FOR YOU TO TAKE ORDERS

22:53.125 --> 22:55.583
WHEN YOU FEEL THAT YOU SHOULD BE
GIVING THEM,

22:55.583 --> 22:58.041
AND I REALLY APPRECIATE
YOUR PROFESSIONALISM.

22:58.041 --> 23:00.500
THANKS. THANK YOU.

23:02.917 --> 23:05.667
YOU DON'T LIKE ROSES?

23:05.667 --> 23:07.792
ALLERGIES.

23:07.792 --> 23:09.917
AND LET ME KNOW WHAT YOU FIND
OUT ABOUT THAT BODY.

23:12.583 --> 23:14.417
OKAY, GUYS, LISTEN UP.

23:14.417 --> 23:17.166
[ INDISTINCT CHATTER
ON POLICE RADIO ]

23:21.375 --> 23:23.667
HEARD YOUR SISTER'S BACK
ON THE JOB ALREADY.

23:23.667 --> 23:25.375
IS SHE IN
ANY KIND OF SHAPE?

23:25.375 --> 23:27.250
OH, YOU KNOW DEB.
NOTHING GETS HER DOWN.

23:27.250 --> 23:30.041
NO, I MEAN, DID SHE PACK ON
ANY POUNDS WHILE SHE WAS GONE?

23:30.041 --> 23:32.041
'CAUSE LAST TIME I SAW HER,
SHE WAS TIGHT.

23:34.041 --> 23:38.542
WE GOT MULTIPLE CHOP WOUNDS,
PRETTY MUCH HEAD TO TOE.

23:38.542 --> 23:41.709
ALL RIGHT, YOU CALL IT --
HEADS OR TAILS.

23:41.709 --> 23:44.375
HEADS.
HEY, I DIDN'T FLIP YET.

23:44.375 --> 23:45.834
YOU SAID "CALL IT."

23:45.834 --> 23:48.250
DAMN.
I ALWAYS GET THE ASS END.

23:48.250 --> 23:50.834
THERE YOU GO, SERGEANT.

23:50.834 --> 23:52.208
NEVER MIND.

23:55.375 --> 23:57.875
I GOT SHARP-FORCE
TRAUMA HERE,

23:57.875 --> 23:59.709
HEAVY-IMPACT,
PARALLEL WOUNDS --

23:59.709 --> 24:01.375
MAYBE AN AX.

24:01.375 --> 24:04.250
NO, THE DEFENSE WOUNDS ON THE
FOREARMS ARE LONG AND LINEAR,

24:04.250 --> 24:06.417
AND I CAN MAKE OUT
BEVELED MARGINS.

24:06.417 --> 24:07.792
A MACHETE DID THIS.

24:07.792 --> 24:11.417
THE MACHETE IS THE WEAPON OF
CHOICE OF THE 29th STREET KINGS.

24:11.417 --> 24:14.083
THE VICTIM WAS IN THE GANG,
JUDGING FROM THAT TATTOO.

24:14.083 --> 24:16.792
WE THINK THE BODY WAS CARRIED
FROM A NEARBY LOCATION.

24:16.792 --> 24:19.875
I FOUND A REAL GOOD BLOOD TRAIL
COMING DOWN FROM THE ROAD.

24:19.875 --> 24:21.333
DAMN IT.

24:21.333 --> 24:23.250
Psst. Psst.

24:23.250 --> 24:24.667
LENS.

24:24.667 --> 24:26.208
[ SIGHS ]

24:26.208 --> 24:28.083
OH.

24:28.083 --> 24:31.333
Doakes:
LET'S MAKE SURE WE CHECK THE
DOCK SLIPS FOR CRIMINAL RECORDS.

24:31.333 --> 24:33.125
IT'S POSSIBLE
THIS VICTIM WAS KILLED

24:33.125 --> 24:34.959
BY ONE OF THESE BOAT OWNERS
OUT HERE.

24:34.959 --> 24:36.667
OR MAYBE IT WAS JUST
AN EASY ACCESS SPOT

24:36.667 --> 24:38.083
TO DUMP A CORPSE
AT NIGHT.

24:38.083 --> 24:39.291
THERE ARE NO LIGHT POLES.

24:39.291 --> 24:41.291
THE FREEWAY EXIT RAMP'S
JUST A BLOCK AWAY.

24:41.291 --> 24:42.458
HE'S GOT A POINT.

24:44.792 --> 24:46.458
YO, DEX.

24:49.083 --> 24:50.458
[ SIGHS ]

24:50.458 --> 24:53.792
YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO PRESERVE
THE CRIME SCENE, ASSHOLE.

24:53.792 --> 24:55.750
[ LAUGHS ]

24:55.750 --> 24:59.417
MAN, WHAT'S THE MATTER
WITH YOU TODAY?

24:59.417 --> 25:03.333
I'M JUST A LITTLE OFF MY GAME.
I'LL GET IT BACK.

25:04.959 --> 25:07.250
WHAT TIME
DID YOU FIND THE BODY?
7:00.

25:07.250 --> 25:10.083
I START PREPPING THE BANANA BOAT
EVERY MORNING AT 7:00

25:10.083 --> 25:11.250
FOR OUR MIAMI BANANA TOUR.

25:11.250 --> 25:13.625
BANANA TOUR?
YEAH, YEAH.

25:13.625 --> 25:16.000
IT'S A CALYPSO JOURNEY
THROUGH MIAMI'S INNER HARBOR,

25:16.000 --> 25:17.166
AND YOU SHOULD TRY IT.

25:17.166 --> 25:18.625
I'LL THINK ABOUT IT.

25:18.625 --> 25:21.667
HEY, ISN'T THAT
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER'S BABE?

25:21.667 --> 25:23.583
SHE WAS IN THE PAPER.
SHE'S FUCKING HOT.

25:23.583 --> 25:25.875
DID YOU SEE ANYONE ELSE
OUT HERE THIS MORNING?

25:25.875 --> 25:27.875
NO, NOT THIS MORNING.

25:27.875 --> 25:29.875
ARE YOU SURE?

25:29.875 --> 25:32.000
YEAH. I'D HAVE GIVEN THEM
A BROCHURE.

25:32.000 --> 25:33.792
YO,
MRS. ICE-TRUCK KILLER!

25:33.792 --> 25:35.625
HANG ON. HANG ON.

25:35.625 --> 25:38.458
JUST TURN AROUND.
LOOK SCARED FOR THE CAMERA.

25:39.625 --> 25:42.000
WELL, IF YOU THINK OF ANYTHING
ELSE, YOU HAVE OUR NUMBERS.

25:42.000 --> 25:44.375
AND YOU HAVE MINE.
CAN I PASS THESE OUT NOW?

25:44.375 --> 25:45.875
KNOCK YOURSELF OUT.

25:45.875 --> 25:47.583
THANK YOU.

25:47.583 --> 25:50.125
COME ON.
JUST LOOK OVER HERE.

25:50.125 --> 25:52.166
LOOK SCARED
FOR THE CAMERA.

25:54.834 --> 25:56.000
MORGAN --

25:58.083 --> 26:00.667
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]
THANK YOU.

26:00.667 --> 26:04.291
WHAT? DO YOU NEED HELP
WITH SOMETHING?

26:04.291 --> 26:06.500
[ SIREN WAILS ]

26:07.667 --> 26:09.667
RAFAEL!

26:09.667 --> 26:13.208
SHIT. SERGEANT!

26:13.208 --> 26:15.125
Doakes: GRAB HER!
DON'T JUST STAND THERE!

26:15.125 --> 26:16.458
GRAB HER!
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

26:16.458 --> 26:18.041
SOMEBODY STOP HER!

26:18.041 --> 26:19.375
RAFAEL!

26:19.375 --> 26:20.709
MISS,
YOU CANNOT GO DOWN THERE.

26:20.709 --> 26:22.291
Doakes: HEY! HEY!

26:22.291 --> 26:23.333
STOP HER!

26:23.333 --> 26:24.917
GOD DAMN IT,
MORGAN, GRAB HER!

26:24.917 --> 26:27.750
[ CRIES ]

26:28.959 --> 26:32.959
LITTLE CHINO HIZO ESTO.

26:32.959 --> 26:35.417
LE HIZO ESO A MI HIJO.

26:35.417 --> 26:38.917
POR FAVOR, ENCUéNTRALO
Y MáTALO COMO PERRO.

26:38.917 --> 26:40.959
TE LO RUEGO.

26:40.959 --> 26:43.417
SEÑORA. SEÑORA.

26:43.417 --> 26:45.458
LO SIENTO MUCHO
SU PéRDIDA, SEÑORA,

26:45.458 --> 26:46.959
PERO TIENE QUE VENIR CONMIGO.

26:46.959 --> 26:49.709
[ CRYING ]

26:49.709 --> 26:51.750
AYúDAME.

26:51.750 --> 26:55.250
CAN WE PLEASE SECURE THIS
MOTHERFUCKING CRIME SCENE?

26:59.750 --> 27:02.417
TEN CUIDADO.
CUIDADO.

27:02.417 --> 27:04.166
WHAT DID SHE SAY?

27:04.166 --> 27:06.750
THAT'S HER SON.

27:06.750 --> 27:09.500
SHE SAYS SHE KNOWS
WHO KILLED HIM --

27:09.500 --> 27:12.625
SOME GUY NAMED
LITTLE CHINO.

27:12.625 --> 27:15.625
IT FELT LIKE SHE WAS
ASKING ME SOMETHING.

27:15.625 --> 27:18.542
SHE WAS -- SHE WANTS YOU
TO FIND LITTLE CHINO

27:18.542 --> 27:20.375
AND KILL HIM LIKE A DOG.

27:20.375 --> 27:23.750
Child:
¿DóNDE ESTá RAFAEL?

27:23.750 --> 27:25.959
¿NO LO ENCONTRó?

27:25.959 --> 27:28.750
[ CRIES ]

27:30.959 --> 27:34.291
Dexter: THAT LOOK.

27:34.291 --> 27:36.542
I KNOW THAT LOOK.

27:36.542 --> 27:40.250
LIKE HER MOTHER, SHE WANTS
SOMEONE TO DO SOMETHING.

27:47.417 --> 27:49.917
Paul: THE NEXT STOP
ON MATCHY THE MATCHBOOK'S

27:49.917 --> 27:53.792
MAGICAL JOURNEY
DOWN THE RAINBOW PATH IS...

27:53.792 --> 27:54.959
[ GASPS ]

27:54.959 --> 27:56.709
...THE DREADED
CHOCOLATE SWAMP.

27:56.709 --> 27:59.250
Astor:
WHY IS IT DREADED?

27:59.250 --> 28:00.750
I LOVE CHOCOLATE.

28:00.750 --> 28:04.667
BECAUSE...THE CHOCOLATE SWAMP
IS THE HOME

28:04.667 --> 28:08.125
OF A GOOPY, GOOEY NIGHTMARE
NAMED GLOPPY,

28:08.125 --> 28:10.625
WHO TURNS CHILDREN
INTO FUDGESICLES AND EATS THEM!

28:10.625 --> 28:12.250
AAH!

28:12.250 --> 28:14.000
WHAT DOES MATCHY DO?

28:16.208 --> 28:19.834
WELL, LUCKILY,
GLOPPY WAS SLEEPING,

28:19.834 --> 28:22.792
SO MATCHY GOES STRAIGHT
TO CANDY CASTLE,

28:22.792 --> 28:24.500
WHERE HE BECOMES KING CANDY,

28:24.500 --> 28:27.208
WHO CAN TURN EVERYONE
INTO SWEETS

28:27.208 --> 28:29.709
WITH A WAVE
OF HIS ROYAL GUMBALL STAFF.

28:29.709 --> 28:31.875
COOL STORY, DAD.

28:31.875 --> 28:34.333
BUT NEXT TIME,
CAN WE PLAY THE ACTUAL GAME?

28:34.333 --> 28:36.709
FIRST CHANCE I GET,
I'LL TALK TO THE WARDEN

28:36.709 --> 28:39.417
ABOUT FINDING SOME OF
THOSE MISSING GAME PIECES, OKAY?

28:40.709 --> 28:44.542
OKAY. GOT TO GO, KIDS.

28:47.333 --> 28:49.458
SAY GOODBYE TO YOUR FATHER.

28:49.458 --> 28:51.417
JUMP! JUMP!
[ GROWLS ]

28:51.417 --> 28:53.041
[ CHUCKLES ]

28:53.041 --> 28:55.083
HUGS! GRR!

28:55.083 --> 28:57.041
WHAT'S WRONG
WITH YOUR LIP?

28:57.041 --> 29:01.375
WELL, I WAS BITING IT
'CAUSE I WAS EXCITED TO SEE YOU.

29:01.375 --> 29:03.458
SO COME BACK REAL SOON, OKAY?

29:03.458 --> 29:05.166
OKAY, BUDDY. BYE.

29:06.375 --> 29:08.375
RITA, ONE MINUTE?

29:08.375 --> 29:10.500
[ SIGHS ]

29:10.500 --> 29:12.542
ALL RIGHT.
GO WAIT BY THE DOOR.

29:14.250 --> 29:15.917
I NEED YOUR HELP.

29:15.917 --> 29:17.750
MY MOTHER IS GONNA FILE
MY APPEAL TOMORROW,

29:17.750 --> 29:19.667
BUT I DON'T STAND A CHANCE
WITHOUT THAT SHOE.

29:19.667 --> 29:22.417
THERE'S NO SHOE. HOW MANY TIMES
DO I HAVE TO TELL YOU THAT?

29:22.417 --> 29:24.834
OKAY...
ANYTHING, ANY EVIDENCE

29:24.834 --> 29:27.875
TO SUPPORT THE FACT
THAT I WAS SET UP.

29:27.875 --> 29:30.291
YOU MEAN
THAT DEXTER SET YOU UP.

29:30.291 --> 29:31.667
SOMEBODY SET ME UP.

29:31.667 --> 29:35.583
RITA, I'M NOT DOING REAL GOOD
IN HERE, OKAY?

29:35.583 --> 29:38.667
IT'S A FEDERAL PRISON,
HARD CORE.

29:38.667 --> 29:40.667
I DON'T BELONG HERE.

29:40.667 --> 29:42.041
WILL YOU HELP ME?

29:44.208 --> 29:47.917
I NEED TO GO.
I'LL SEE YOU IN A COUPLE WEEKS.

29:50.000 --> 29:53.083
[ SIGHS ]

29:53.083 --> 29:55.291
LeGuerta: LE VAMOS A HACER
UNAS CUANTAS PREGUNTAS.

29:55.291 --> 29:57.375
EH, HASTA QUE COMUNICó.

29:57.375 --> 30:01.125
ANGEL, WILL YOU PLEASE
TAKE EVA'S STATEMENT

30:01.125 --> 30:03.000
AND SET UP HER DAUGHTER,
MARISSA,

30:03.000 --> 30:04.458
WITH SOME CRAYONS, OKAY?

30:04.458 --> 30:06.792
Batista: SURE THING.

30:06.792 --> 30:08.792
ME LLAMO ANGEL.

30:08.792 --> 30:11.458
LO SIENTO MUCHO,
LA PéRDIDA DE TU HIJO.

30:12.291 --> 30:13.583
VENTE.

30:19.458 --> 30:22.417
THAT GIRL'S GONNA NEED
MORE THAN CRAYONS

30:22.417 --> 30:23.959
TO MAKE HER WORLD RIGHT.

30:23.959 --> 30:28.667
KILLING LITTLE CHINO
COULD RESTORE MY WORLD, TOO,

30:28.667 --> 30:32.083
BUT ONLY IF HE SATISFIES
HARRY'S CODE.

30:34.583 --> 30:35.875
I SEE YOU'VE BEEN BENCHED.

30:35.875 --> 30:37.291
LaGUERTA'S JUST JEALOUS

30:37.291 --> 30:40.083
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER FUCKED ME
INSTEAD OF HER.

30:40.083 --> 30:42.333
WOW.

30:42.333 --> 30:43.834
YOU'RE CHIPPER.

30:43.834 --> 30:45.792
JUST HAPPY TO BE BACK
ON THE JOB.

30:48.000 --> 30:49.375
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

30:49.375 --> 30:52.208
JUST WORKING UP MY BLOOD REPORT
FROM THE CRIME SCENE TODAY,

30:52.208 --> 30:55.083
WANTED TO KNOW WHAT YOU FOUND ON
THE SUSPECT LITTLE CHINO.

30:55.083 --> 30:56.834
COCKSUCKER'S GUILTY
AS THEY COME.

30:56.834 --> 30:59.625
HE'S AN ENFORCER
FOR THE 29th STREET KINGS,

30:59.625 --> 31:01.500
EAST SIDE GANG,
INTENSELY VIOLENT.

31:01.500 --> 31:05.166
HE'S BEEN LINKED TO NINE MURDERS
IN THE LAST FIVE YEARS.

31:05.166 --> 31:06.500
SO FAR, SO GOOD.

31:06.500 --> 31:08.417
I JUST HOPE HE'S NOT BLIND.

31:08.417 --> 31:10.291
HAS HE EVER BEEN TRIED?

31:10.291 --> 31:13.417
TWICE, BUT THE WITNESSES
IN EACH CASE WERE MURDERED,

31:13.417 --> 31:14.709
WE THINK BY CHINO HIMSELF.

31:14.709 --> 31:16.792
NOW PEOPLE ARE JUST TOO AFRAID
TO COME FORWARD.

31:16.792 --> 31:19.750
Doakes: COME ON, CHINO,
RIGHT THIS WAY.

31:36.375 --> 31:40.166
FUCKING BEEF BUS.

31:46.375 --> 31:47.208
[ GUNSHOT ]

31:47.208 --> 31:49.291
Dexter: DAD!

31:49.291 --> 31:51.333
I'M OKAY, DEX.

31:51.333 --> 31:52.709
I'VE TOLD YOU --

31:52.709 --> 31:54.542
NEVER PUT YOUR FINGER
ON THE TRIGGER

31:54.542 --> 31:55.375
UNLESS YOU'RE SHOOTING.

31:55.375 --> 31:56.750
ARE YOU OKAY?

31:56.750 --> 31:58.709
JESUS, THAT WAS CLOSE.

31:58.709 --> 32:00.542
MY HEART'S BEATING
OUT OF MY CHEST.

32:01.542 --> 32:03.375
LET ME FEEL.

32:03.375 --> 32:04.417
FEEL WHAT?

32:04.417 --> 32:05.542
YOUR HEART.

32:07.458 --> 32:08.542
[ SIGHS ]

32:11.208 --> 32:13.041
THAT'S AMAZING.

32:16.417 --> 32:19.458
A CHALLENGE,
A MOUNTAIN TO CLIMB.

32:19.458 --> 32:21.083
I NEED THIS ONE.

32:21.083 --> 32:24.750
Eva: LITTLE CHINO CAME
TO MY FRONT DOOR.

32:24.750 --> 32:28.250
HE ASKED FOR MY SON,
RAFAEL.

32:28.250 --> 32:32.333
RAFAEL DID NOT WANT TO GO
WITH LITTLE CHINO,

32:32.333 --> 32:35.291
BUT HE WAS AFRAID
NOT TO.

32:35.291 --> 32:37.542
Batista:
WHAT WAS HE GOING TO DO?

32:37.542 --> 32:40.208
[ Crying ] MY BROTHER HAS
A HOUSE IN GEORGIA.

32:40.208 --> 32:42.792
RAFAEL WAS GOING TO LIVE
WITH HIM.

32:42.792 --> 32:45.417
THAT'S WHY THEY KILL HIM.

32:45.417 --> 32:46.917
I KNOW IT.

32:46.917 --> 32:50.291
NOBODY EVER LEAVES
THE GANG.

32:50.291 --> 32:51.625
EVA. EVA.

32:51.625 --> 32:53.375
EVA.

32:53.375 --> 32:56.125
ARE YOU WILLING TO TESTIFY

32:56.125 --> 32:58.250
THAT LITTLE CHINO PICKED UP
YOUR SON

32:58.250 --> 32:59.667
ON THE NIGHT OF HIS DEATH?

33:01.291 --> 33:03.458
COME ON.
DON'T BACK DOWN NOW.

33:03.458 --> 33:06.083
[ CRYING ]

33:06.083 --> 33:10.000
Sí.
I WANT HIM TO PAY.

33:11.917 --> 33:13.625
GOT HIM.

33:13.625 --> 33:15.959
WELL, THAT'S DISCOURAGING.

33:15.959 --> 33:18.625
WITH A GRIEVING MOTHER
AS A WITNESS,

33:18.625 --> 33:21.917
LITTLE CHINO WILL NEVER REACH
MY CUTTING COURTROOM.

33:27.291 --> 33:30.333
HEY, MORGAN, YOU WANT TO SEE
SOMETHING SWELL?

33:30.333 --> 33:31.834
COME A LITTLE CLOSER.

33:31.834 --> 33:35.792
AND THE TOKEN HAS SPOKEN.
GOOD TO SEE YOU, TOO, VINCE.

33:35.792 --> 33:38.667
I, UH, HEARD
WE CAPTURED BIGFOOT.

33:38.667 --> 33:42.208
BEHOLD THE EIGHTH WONDER
OF THE WORLD.

33:42.208 --> 33:44.291
AM I SPEAKING CLEARLY?

33:44.291 --> 33:45.792
[ LAUGHS ]

33:50.792 --> 33:51.917
YEAH.

33:51.917 --> 33:54.417
THEN ANSWER MY FUCKING QUESTION,
CHINO.

33:54.417 --> 33:56.667
WHAT TIME DID YOU PICK UP RAFAEL
LAST NIGHT?

33:56.667 --> 34:01.375
LAST NIGHT?
I DIDN'T SEE RAFAEL LAST NIGHT.

34:01.375 --> 34:03.834
OKAY, SO WHY WOULD
RAFAEL'S MOTHER

34:03.834 --> 34:05.875
MAKE UP THAT STORY,
CHINO?

34:05.875 --> 34:07.500
[ CHUCKLES ]

34:07.500 --> 34:09.250
THAT PUTA'S INTO
THE DEVIL'S CANDY, MAN --

34:09.250 --> 34:10.542
FUCKING HEROIN.

34:10.542 --> 34:11.709
SHIT.

34:11.709 --> 34:13.959
SHE WAS PROBABLY HIGH.

34:13.959 --> 34:16.041
YOU'RE TELLING ME
THAT EVA ARENAS IS A JUNKIE?

34:16.041 --> 34:18.000
Debra:
OH, MAN, IF THAT'S TRUE,

34:18.000 --> 34:20.417
PASCAL AND LaGUERTA ARE GONNA
HAVE A PISS PARTY.

34:23.375 --> 34:25.458
EVA ARENAS,
TWO POPS FOR DRUG POSSESSION.

34:25.458 --> 34:28.083
NO FUCKING WAY THE D.A. PUTS
A DRUG USER ON THE STAND.

34:28.083 --> 34:30.709
THAT CHOLO'S GONNA
WALK AGAIN.

34:30.709 --> 34:33.041
BUT NOT VERY FAR.

34:38.125 --> 34:42.041
WE'LL BOTH BE VINDICATED SOON.

35:13.417 --> 35:16.291
Woman:
Okay, boys, today's our day.

35:16.291 --> 35:20.208
Let's find that galleon
and bring back the gold.

35:22.583 --> 35:25.041
Here's that aberration
in the seafloor.

35:25.041 --> 35:27.458
The crevice is at 65 feet.

35:27.458 --> 35:29.250
It has to be
where the Santa Rosa  went down.

35:43.792 --> 35:47.083
The crevice is 30 to 40 yards
straight ahead.

35:50.625 --> 35:54.834
[ METAL DETECTOR CRACKLING ]

36:12.500 --> 36:17.458
The crevice should be 25 yards
ahead, bearing 1-4-4.

36:59.875 --> 37:01.250
I NEED YOUR HELP.

37:01.250 --> 37:04.083
I KNOW HOW MUCH YOU WERE LOOKING
FORWARD TO GOING OUT TONIGHT,

37:04.083 --> 37:05.709
BUT I THINK DEB
COULD USE YOU MORE.

37:05.709 --> 37:08.834
NOW, DEXTER, THIS ISN'T
ABOUT THIS MORNING, IS IT?

37:08.834 --> 37:10.542
NO, NO, I SWEAR.
NO, THIS IS FOR DEB.

37:10.542 --> 37:12.208
SHE HAD HER FIRST DAY
AT WORK TODAY,

37:12.208 --> 37:14.208
AND LaGUERTA WAS KIND OF ROUGH
ON HER.

37:14.208 --> 37:16.542
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]
Debra:
DEXTER, UNLOCK THE DOOR.

37:16.542 --> 37:17.542
HOLD ON.

37:17.542 --> 37:19.875
HOLD ON!

37:19.875 --> 37:23.542
DEXTER, COME ON!
OPEN THE FUCKING DOOR!

37:23.542 --> 37:25.542
SEE,
SHE'S YELLING AT ME NOW.

37:25.542 --> 37:26.875
LOOK, I'M NO EXPERT,

37:26.875 --> 37:29.959
BUT I THINK DEB COULD USE
SOME GIRL TIME TONIGHT.

37:29.959 --> 37:31.208
WELL, I WON'T LIE.

37:31.208 --> 37:33.041
I'M A LITTLE DISAPPOINTED,

37:33.041 --> 37:35.834
BUT I KNOW YOUR HEART'S
IN THE RIGHT PLACE.

37:35.834 --> 37:38.417
ABSOLUTELY.
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

37:38.417 --> 37:40.583
OKAY.
WHATEVER YOU NEED, DEXTER.

37:40.583 --> 37:42.583
THANK YOU, RITA.
I WILL MAKE THIS UP TO YOU.

37:42.583 --> 37:44.959
I'M GONNA HAVE DEB PICK YOU UP
IN A HALF-HOUR, OKAY?

37:44.959 --> 37:45.959
BYE.

37:45.959 --> 37:48.417
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

37:48.417 --> 37:49.875
SORRY.

37:49.875 --> 37:52.291
I, UH, DOUBLE-BOOKED

37:52.291 --> 37:54.375
WHEN I MADE PLANS
TO GO OUT WITH RITA TONIGHT.

37:54.375 --> 37:57.583
I FORGOT THAT I HAD PROMISED
TO SUB FOR ANOTHER BOWLING TEAM.

37:57.583 --> 37:59.583
WHY DO YOU LOOK SO HAPPY
ABOUT IT?

37:59.583 --> 38:01.375
I LIKE BOWLING.
WHAT CAN I SAY?

38:01.375 --> 38:03.625
LOOK, WILL YOU TAKE RITA OUT
FOR ME?

38:03.625 --> 38:05.333
SHE HIRED A BABYSITTER
AND EVERYTHING.

38:05.333 --> 38:06.750
NO WAY.
I NEED TO WORK OUT.

38:06.750 --> 38:08.291
ACTUALLY, YOU NEED TO STOP
WORKING OUT.

38:08.291 --> 38:09.583
IT'S GETTING UNHEALTHY.

38:09.583 --> 38:11.750
WHY DON'T YOU GO OUT
FOR SOME HARD LIQUOR INSTEAD?

38:11.750 --> 38:13.125
MNH-MNH.

38:13.125 --> 38:15.000
SORRY, BRO.
DEB, PLEASE.

38:16.834 --> 38:20.000
WHEN DO I EVER ASK YOU
FOR ANYTHING?

38:20.000 --> 38:22.166
[ TREADMILL BEEPS ]

38:23.208 --> 38:25.667
YOU BUNGHOLE. WHY'D YOU HAVE TO
PUT IT THAT WAY?

38:25.667 --> 38:27.792
SHE'S EXPECTING YOU
IN A HALF AN HOUR.

38:27.792 --> 38:29.125
YOU'RE A LIFESAVER.

38:36.458 --> 38:38.792
TONIGHT'S THE NIGHT.

38:38.792 --> 38:41.333
REALLY.

38:41.333 --> 38:44.208
HARRY WOULD PREFER
I TAKE MORE TIME,

38:44.208 --> 38:47.125
BUT MY LIFE IS FALLING APART.

38:49.250 --> 38:52.291
WHATEVER STOPPED MY KNIFE
BEFORE WON'T STOP IT AGAIN.

38:52.291 --> 38:55.083
HEY, THERE!

38:55.083 --> 38:58.208
GONNA WORK
ON MY RELEASE TONIGHT --

38:58.208 --> 39:01.083
PRACTICE,
PRACTICE, PRACTICE.

39:01.083 --> 39:04.125
LANE'S OPEN TILL MIDNIGHT.
YOU WANT TO JOIN ME?

39:12.250 --> 39:14.166
[ SIGHS ] FUCK IT.

39:14.166 --> 39:17.125
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

39:20.709 --> 39:23.417
[ BRAKES SQUEAL ]

39:23.417 --> 39:25.375
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

39:34.000 --> 39:36.000
[ GROANS ]

39:38.166 --> 39:39.667
MMM.

39:48.041 --> 39:50.041
[ ELEVATOR DINGS ]

39:50.041 --> 39:52.542
THERE IS NOTHING ELSE
TO TALK ABOUT.

39:52.542 --> 39:54.750
YOU ARE A LIAR,
AND YOU LIED!

39:54.750 --> 39:57.709
Bertrand: WOULD YOU STOP TRYING
TO ACT ALL HARD LIKE THAT?

39:57.709 --> 40:00.792
YOU WANT ME TO ACT BETTER,
THEN YOU TREAT ME BETTER.

40:00.792 --> 40:03.667
YOU GOT THESE THINGS
ALL MIXED UP IN YOUR HEAD.

40:03.667 --> 40:05.375
LISTEN TO ME.
I LOVE YOU, BOO.

40:05.375 --> 40:08.000
IT'S ALL ABOUT YOU.
THERE IS NOBODY ELSE!

40:08.000 --> 40:11.542
IS THAT WHY YOU SENT ME
THREE DOZEN FUCKING ROSES?

40:11.542 --> 40:13.417
[ SCOFFS ]
GET OUT OF MY SIGHT.

40:13.417 --> 40:16.166
I SEND YOU FLOWERS, BABE,
BECAUSE I LOVE YOU.

40:16.166 --> 40:17.875
GET OUT OF MY SIGHT,
BERTRAND.

40:17.875 --> 40:21.291
I GOT NOTHING ELSE TO SAY TO YOU
UNTIL YOU DECIDE TO MAN UP.

40:21.291 --> 40:23.709
PLEASE GO.

40:27.834 --> 40:30.875
[ ELEVATOR DINGS ]

40:33.250 --> 40:35.333
MARIA?

40:35.333 --> 40:37.083
FUCK.

40:45.125 --> 40:46.959
I'M SORRY
YOU HAD TO HEAR THAT.

40:46.959 --> 40:49.709
THAT WAS MY FIANCé.

40:49.709 --> 40:53.250
WE ARE HAVING
SOME PROBLEMS.

40:53.250 --> 40:56.583
WELL, THAT HAPPENS.

41:04.458 --> 41:06.875
I CALLED HIS HOUSE THREE NIGHTS
IN A ROW,

41:06.875 --> 41:08.583
AND HE SAYS
THAT HE'S WORKING.

41:08.583 --> 41:10.542
HE DOESN'T RETURN
MY PHONE CALLS.

41:10.542 --> 41:12.959
AND THEN HE COMES HOME,
AND HE SAYS HE'S TIRED.

41:12.959 --> 41:14.500
[ SCOFFS ]

41:14.500 --> 41:18.000
WELL, HE'S TIRED BECAUSE HE'S
OUT THERE FUCKING SOME BITCH.

41:18.000 --> 41:20.959
I CAN SMELL IT ON HIM.

41:20.959 --> 41:22.834
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

41:22.834 --> 41:25.208
DON'T WORRY
ABOUT WASHING THEIR HAIR,

41:25.208 --> 41:26.959
AND READ TO THEM BEFORE BED.

41:26.959 --> 41:29.750
OKAY, GOT IT.

41:29.750 --> 41:30.792
HELLO?

41:30.792 --> 41:32.750
You have a collect call
from Paul Bennett.

41:32.750 --> 41:33.959
Will you accept the charges?

41:33.959 --> 41:35.250
YES, I'LL ACCEPT
THE CHARGES.

41:37.959 --> 41:39.834
EXCUSE ME.

41:39.834 --> 41:43.000
Rita, do you have a second?
I need to talk to you.

41:43.000 --> 41:44.000
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

41:44.000 --> 41:46.166
I'M NOT GONNA MAKE IT
IN HERE.

41:46.166 --> 41:49.250
I DON'T HAVE TIME FOR
YOUR BULLSHIT RIGHT NOW, PAUL.

41:49.250 --> 41:50.667
It's not bullshit.

41:50.667 --> 41:53.333
I'M NOT LIKE THESE GUYS.
I DON'T BELONG HERE, RITA.

41:53.333 --> 41:54.709
CAN YOU HELP ME?

41:54.709 --> 41:56.667
HELP YOU? WHAT?

41:56.667 --> 42:00.625
JUST, CAN YOU LOOK
FOR THE SHOE ONE MORE TIME?

42:00.625 --> 42:04.333
[ SIGHS ] I FOUND
THE FUCKING SHOE, OKAY?

42:04.333 --> 42:07.083
YOU WHAT? YOU WHAT?

42:07.083 --> 42:09.834
OH, THAT'S GREAT! I'LL CALL
THE LAWYER IN THE MORNING!

42:09.834 --> 42:11.959
LOOK, WHAT DOES IT MATTER?
IT'S JUST A SHOE.

42:11.959 --> 42:13.417
IT DOESN'T MEAN ANYTHING.

42:13.417 --> 42:16.166
YOU WERE PROBABLY HIGH ON SMACK
WHEN YOU LOST IT AT MY HOUSE.

42:16.166 --> 42:19.083
WHATEVER, WHATEVER. I'LL LET
THE COURTS FUCKING DECIDE THAT.

42:19.083 --> 42:20.166
THIS IS GOOD NEWS.

42:20.166 --> 42:21.667
No! No, Paul, no.

42:21.667 --> 42:24.333
IF YOU SEND A LAWYER TO MY
HOUSE, THE SHOE WON'T BE HERE.

42:24.333 --> 42:26.542
I am not gonna let you
drag Dexter into this.

42:26.542 --> 42:28.291
I'M IN A HEALTHY RELATIONSHIP,
FINALLY,

42:28.291 --> 42:29.709
AND I'M NOT GONNA
THROW IT AWAY

42:29.709 --> 42:31.250
TO BAIL OUT
MY ABUSIVE EX-HUSBAND.

42:31.250 --> 42:33.458
It doesn't work that way.

42:33.458 --> 42:35.041
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]
I GOT TO GO.

42:35.041 --> 42:36.583
NO, YOU DON'T.
NO, DON'T --

42:36.583 --> 42:38.542
RITA, DON'T HANG UP
THAT FUCKING PHONE.

42:38.542 --> 42:40.583
STOP BLAMING OTHER PEOPLE
FOR YOUR PROBLEMS.

42:40.583 --> 42:43.000
YOU'RE IN PRISON NOW, PAUL.
DEAL WITH IT.

42:43.000 --> 42:44.041
Rita!

42:44.041 --> 42:49.000
UGH! UGH! NO!
NO! NO! NO!

42:52.375 --> 42:55.834
[ BUZZING ]

42:55.834 --> 42:59.375
SOME GANGS EARN
TEARDROPS OF BLOOD BY KILLING.

42:59.375 --> 43:02.041
I UNDERSTAND.
WE ALL NEED OUR KEEPSAKES.

43:02.041 --> 43:05.750
ONE MAN'S TATTOOS ARE
ANOTHER MAN'S BLOOD SLIDES.

43:05.750 --> 43:07.750
ALL I HAD TO DO WAS CALL
THE GANG TASK FORCE,

43:07.750 --> 43:10.500
ASK WHERE THE 29th STREET KINGS
GET THEIR TATTOOS,

43:10.500 --> 43:13.750
AND WAIT FOR MY PREY
TO SHOW UP.

43:19.500 --> 43:21.625
[ CHICKENS CLUCKING ]
WHAT THE FUCK?

43:23.083 --> 43:25.583
WHAT THE FUCK?
GET THE FUCK OFF ME!

43:25.583 --> 43:27.792
FUCK! GET THE FUCK OFF!

43:27.792 --> 43:29.208
[ CHICKENS CLUCKING ]

43:29.208 --> 43:31.625
FUCK THAT SHIT!

43:44.250 --> 43:46.000
[ GROANS ]

43:46.000 --> 43:48.125
THE SCENE
OF THE FAILED CRIME --

43:48.125 --> 43:49.959
NO BETTER PLACE TO TRY AGAIN.

43:49.959 --> 43:52.959
I HAVE IT ON GOOD AUTHORITY
THE OWNER FLED TOWN.

43:52.959 --> 43:55.375
PLUS, IT'S A MUCH QUIETER
WORKING ENVIRONMENT NOW

43:55.375 --> 43:56.917
WITHOUT THE CHICKENS.

44:08.959 --> 44:10.917
[ STRAINING ]

44:14.625 --> 44:16.542
SO...

44:16.542 --> 44:19.625
YOU AND DEXTER
COME HERE A LOT?

44:19.625 --> 44:21.000
WE LOVE THE HOT WINGS.

44:23.458 --> 44:25.500
[ SIGHS ]

44:25.500 --> 44:28.583
LOOK, I'M SORRY IF I'M SUCH
BAD COMPANY TONIGHT.

44:28.583 --> 44:30.959
PAUL CALLED
RIGHT BEFORE WE LEFT.

44:30.959 --> 44:33.125
YEAH?
WHAT DID HE WANT?

44:33.125 --> 44:34.375
WELL, WHO KNOWS?

44:34.375 --> 44:36.542
MAKE ME FEEL BAD
HE'S IN PRISON, I SUPPOSE.

44:36.542 --> 44:38.041
HEY,
I'M THE ONE THAT ANSWERED

44:38.041 --> 44:40.542
THAT DOMESTIC-DISPUTE CALL
WAY BACK WHEN, REMEMBER?

44:40.542 --> 44:43.375
THAT PRICK DESERVES TO BE
IN PRISON.

44:43.375 --> 44:45.291
I KNOW. I KNOW.

44:45.291 --> 44:47.375
I KNOW. I JUST --
[ GROANS ]

44:47.375 --> 44:49.500
I CAN'T BELIEVE
I STILL LET HIM GET TO ME

44:49.500 --> 44:51.542
AFTER EVERYTHING
HE'S PUT ME THROUGH.

44:54.875 --> 44:57.959
OH, GOD,
I'M SUCH AN IDIOT.

44:57.959 --> 45:00.834
WHAT YOU WENT THROUGH IS
SO MUCH WORSE THAN MY PROBLEMS.

45:00.834 --> 45:04.542
WHAT --
MY PSYCHO KILLER FIANCé?

45:04.542 --> 45:07.542
PLEASE.
I'VE HAD WORSE.

45:07.542 --> 45:09.667
AT LEAST
HE PAID FOR MY MEALS.

45:09.667 --> 45:10.875
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

45:10.875 --> 45:13.375
I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU MOVED ON
LIKE THAT.

45:13.375 --> 45:15.417
I WISH I COULD BE
MORE LIKE YOU.

45:15.417 --> 45:21.417
PAUL WAS SO HORRIBLE TO ME...
REALLY HORRIBLE.

45:21.417 --> 45:25.750
SOMETIMES --
DON'T TELL DEXTER,

45:25.750 --> 45:28.750
BUT SOMETIMES...

45:28.750 --> 45:31.917
I FIND MYSELF MISSING
THE GOOD PARTS OF HIM.

45:34.166 --> 45:35.667
[ Chuckling ]
OH, GOD.

45:38.875 --> 45:41.834
NOT HIM.

45:41.834 --> 45:45.959
NOT HIM --
IT'S NOT HIM THAT YOU MISS,

45:45.959 --> 45:49.667
'CAUSE WHAT HE HAD TO OFFER
WASN'T REAL.

45:51.834 --> 45:55.959
BUT THE WAY HE MADE YOU FEEL
ABOUT YOURSELF...

45:58.417 --> 46:01.208
...THAT WAS REAL.

46:01.208 --> 46:03.667
HEY, ARE YOU OKAY?

46:03.667 --> 46:05.917
NEED A REFILL?

46:09.542 --> 46:11.458
[ CHUCKLES ]

46:11.458 --> 46:13.750
CAN I GET ANOTHER DRAFT,
PLEASE?

46:13.750 --> 46:16.000
HEY, EXCUSE ME.

46:16.000 --> 46:18.208
DON'T I KNOW YOU
FROM SOMEWHERE?

46:20.083 --> 46:23.750
HAVEN'T I SEEN YOU
ON TELEVISION?

46:23.750 --> 46:26.417
OH, YEAH.

46:26.417 --> 46:29.542
HEY, EXCUSE ME,
ARE YOU THAT GIRL --

46:29.542 --> 46:31.083
WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU DOING?

46:31.083 --> 46:32.500
DEBRA, WHAT HAPPENED?

46:32.500 --> 46:34.208
HE GRABBED ME.
YOU SAW IT, RIGHT?

46:34.208 --> 46:35.625
HE GRABBED ME.

46:35.625 --> 46:37.542
I THINK YOU BROKE
MY FUCKING NOSE.

46:37.542 --> 46:38.792
YOU FUCKING GRABBED ME!

46:38.792 --> 46:40.291
ALL I DID WAS TOUCH YOU.

46:40.291 --> 46:43.834
YOU SAW IT.
HE GRABBED ME.

46:51.500 --> 46:53.625
HE WASN'T EASY TO GET HERE,

46:53.625 --> 46:56.458
BUT HERE HE IS,
AND HERE I AM --

46:56.458 --> 47:00.917
READY, WILLING...

47:00.917 --> 47:03.583
ABLE?

47:06.834 --> 47:10.458
SHIT, SHIT, SHIT, SHIT, SHIT.

47:10.458 --> 47:12.291
SHIT.

47:14.500 --> 47:18.208
NOT ENOUGH TAPE. PERFECT.

47:18.208 --> 47:20.125
[ STRAINING ]

47:39.834 --> 47:43.250
39 DAYS, 22 HOURS,
AND 18 MINUTES

47:43.250 --> 47:45.834
SINCE I KILLED MY BROTHER.

47:45.834 --> 47:48.208
I  AM  CURSED.

47:50.875 --> 47:52.458
[ WIND GUSTING ]

48:15.792 --> 48:17.458
[ GASPS ]

48:17.458 --> 48:20.500
Harry: HEY! WHAT THE HELL
DO YOU THINK YOU'RE DOING?

48:20.500 --> 48:21.959
WHAT WERE YOU DOING
UP THERE?

48:21.959 --> 48:23.458
I DON'T KNOW.
WHAT WERE YOU THINKING?

48:23.458 --> 48:24.834
I DON'T KNOW.

48:24.834 --> 48:26.375
WHATEVER
YOU'RE GOING THROUGH,

48:26.375 --> 48:28.208
KILLING YOURSELF
ISN'T THE ANSWER, DEX.

48:28.208 --> 48:29.875
YOU DON'T GET POINTS
FOR DYING.

48:29.875 --> 48:31.333
DYING?

48:31.333 --> 48:33.709
DAD,
I DON'T WANT TO DIE.

48:33.709 --> 48:37.000
I'M JUST TRYING TO FIGURE OUT
SOME WAY TO FEEL ALIVE.

48:41.291 --> 48:45.750
I DON'T NORMALLY SEEK HUMAN
CONTACT IN TIMES OF FAILURE,

48:45.750 --> 48:50.375
BUT THEN I DON'T NORMALLY
EXPERIENCE FAILURE.

48:50.375 --> 48:54.500
RIGHT NOW ALL I CAN THINK ABOUT
IS THE SMELL OF RITA'S KITCHEN,

48:54.500 --> 48:58.709
THE BREATHY CADENCE
OF HER SLEEPING CHILDREN,

48:58.709 --> 49:01.542
THE WARMTH OF HER FLESH.

49:08.917 --> 49:12.083
[ RITA CRYING ]

49:23.375 --> 49:25.500
RITA?

49:25.500 --> 49:28.000
WHAT'S WRONG?

49:29.875 --> 49:31.959
THE PRISON CALLED.

49:31.959 --> 49:34.875
PAUL'S DEAD.

49:34.875 --> 49:37.417
OH?

49:41.125 --> 49:43.834
OH.

49:43.834 --> 49:48.333
HE DIED
IN AN INMATE ALTERCATION.

49:48.333 --> 49:50.000
IT WAS A FIGHT.

49:50.000 --> 49:53.959
HE WAS ANGRY,
AND HE GOT INTO A FIGHT.

49:53.959 --> 49:55.792
NOW I HAVE TO FIGURE OUT

49:55.792 --> 49:59.125
HOW TO TELL MY CHILDREN
THEIR FATHER'S DEAD.

50:03.375 --> 50:05.959
AND I COULD HAVE HELPED HIM.

50:08.667 --> 50:10.458
HOW?

50:13.333 --> 50:16.959
RITA, HOW COULD YOU HAVE HELPED
HIM? HE WAS IN PRISON.

50:18.458 --> 50:22.542
THAT'S RIGHT, DEXTER.
IT HAPPENED IN PRISON.

50:22.542 --> 50:25.166
PAUL WAS IN PRISON.

50:28.000 --> 50:29.792
THAT WAS HIS OWN FAULT.

50:34.250 --> 50:36.166
WAS IT?

50:39.166 --> 50:41.375
[ SIGHS ]

50:41.375 --> 50:43.458
[ CRIES ]

50:52.500 --> 50:54.208
[ SOBBING ]

51:09.500 --> 51:11.375
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

51:11.375 --> 51:14.542
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT? RITA SAID YOU
GOT IN A BAR BRAWL TONIGHT.

51:14.542 --> 51:16.125
YOU GOT TO SEE THIS.

51:16.125 --> 51:18.583
Man:
...MT. PLEASANT AND 81...

51:18.583 --> 51:21.917
THEY'VE BEEN PLAYING IT
ON THE NEWS ALL NIGHT.

51:25.125 --> 51:28.083
TWO TREASURE HUNTERS MADE
A GHASTLY DISCOVERY TODAY

51:28.083 --> 51:30.667
WHEN THEY STUMBLED
ON WHAT APPEARS TO BE

51:30.667 --> 51:34.208
AN UNDERWATER GRAVEYARD IN A
CREVICE OFF THE COAST OF MIAMI.

51:34.208 --> 51:35.750
THERE'S BODIES
IN THOSE BAGS.

51:35.750 --> 51:37.417
THE BUTCHERED BODIES
WERE SUBMERGED

51:37.417 --> 51:40.417
INSIDE THESE HEAVY-DUTY
GARBAGE BAGS.

51:40.417 --> 51:43.500
AUTHORITIES HAVE LOCATED
AT LEAST 30 BAGS SO FAR,

51:43.500 --> 51:46.792
BUT AROUND-THE-CLOCK SALVAGE
EFFORTS ARE STILL UNDER WAY.

51:46.792 --> 51:48.959
DID YOU HEAR THAT?
30 BAGS.

51:48.959 --> 51:51.250
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT THAT MEANS?

51:51.250 --> 51:53.792
MEANS THERE MIGHT BE
A NEW MASS MURDERER OUT THERE,

51:53.792 --> 51:56.250
WAY WORSE THAN
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

51:56.250 --> 51:59.583
MAYBE I CAN FINALLY
GET SOME PEACE.

51:59.583 --> 52:01.458
ISN'T THAT GREAT?

52:06.417 --> 52:09.208
IT'S AMAZING.

52:09.208 --> 52:12.834
[ HEART POUNDING ]

52:23.583 --> 52:26.458
